Ecology and distribution. Shelf species found at depths from three (
Stepanjants 1979
) to 471 m (
Peña Cantero & García Carrascosa 1995
). Frequently reported epibiotic on other species of hydroids (
Totton 1930
;
Stepanjants 1979
;
Peña Cantero & García Carrascosa 1995
; Peña Cantero 2008 , 2013;
Peña Cantero & Vervoort 2009
