Stepanjants 1979
), polychaete tubes (
Totton 1930
;
Stepanjants 1979
), and bryozoans (Peña Cantero 2013 ; Peña Cantero et al . 2013 ). Used in turn as substratum for other hydroids (Peña Cantero et al . 2013 ).

